@NotUKNot 

Downgrading my node version to 14.17.6 and my npm version to 6.14.15 let me install truffle. I still get this "Python is not set..." error, but the installation succeeded. And now I am able to use the cli.

It is also mentioned here that it does not work with npm >= 7. See https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/issues/4692#issuecomment-1030092301
